Package algorithms

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Algorithm
    All search algorithms will implement this interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlgorithmBase
    This class contains the implementations of the getRoute and currentReady methods which are identical for all the searchalgorithms.
    AlgorithmFactory
    Used to fetch new instances of the algorithms.
    BestFirstSearch
    This class is used to run a Best-First-Search.
    BreadthFirstSearch
    This class is used to run a Breadth-First-Search.
    DepthFirstSearch
    This class is used to run a Depth-First-Search.
    DijkstraOrAStar
    This class is used to run a Dijkstra's algorithm or a A*-algorithm.
